first_para: Jeremy Richard Browne (born 17 May 1970) is a British Liberal Democrat politician who was the Member of Parliament (MP) for Taunton Deane from 2005 to the dissolution of the 55th Parliament on 30 March 2015.

full.extract:
Jeremy Richard Browne (born 17 May 1970) is a British Liberal Democrat politician who was the Member of Parliament (MP) for Taunton Deane from 2005 to the dissolution of the 55th Parliament on 30 March 2015.
He was previously a Foreign Office and Home Office Minister.
full.title: Jeremy Browne
